data.title: Registration List / Arrived Participants
data.meta_description: 26th General Assembly of the International Astronomical Union (IAU), Prague, 14. - 25. August 2006
data.text: 2.412 participants and 208 accompanying persons has finally arrived to Prague to attend the XXVIth GA IAU. 2.399 people is listed here those who agreed to publish their initials on the web while registered
